\c 22
\s Rwiyo rwaDhavhidhi
\p
\v 1 Zvino Dhavhidhi wakataura kuna Jehovha mashoko orwiyo urwu nenguva yaakarwirwa naJehovha pamaoko avavengi vake vese, napamaoko aSauro;
\v 2 akati: Jehovha idombo rangu, nenhare yangu, nemununuri wangu, iye ndewangu.
\v 3 Mwari wedombo rangu, ndichavimba naye; nhovo yangu, norunyanga rwokuponeswa kwangu, shongwe yangu yakakwirira, noutiziro hwangu. Muponesi wangu, anondiponesa pakumanikidzwa.
\v 4 Ndichadana kuna Jehovha, iye anofanira kurumbidzwa; naizvozvo ndichaponeswa kuna vavengi vangu.
\p
\v 5 Nokuti mafungu orufu akandikomba, uye nzizi dza ezvakaipa dzakandivhundusa.
\v 6 Mabote aSheori akandisunga, misungo yorufu yakandiwira.
\v 7 Pakutambudzika kwangu ndakadana kuna Jehovha, ndakadana kuna Mwari wangu, akanzwa inzwi rangu ari mutemberi yake; kuchema kwangu kukasvika munzeve dzake.
\v 8 Ipapo nyika yakazununguka, ikadedera; nheyo dzokudenga dzakadengenyeka, dzikazununguswa, nokuti iye wakange atsamwa.
\v 9 Utsi hwakakwira huchibva mumhino dzake, uye moto wakabuda mumuromo make, wakaparadza; mazimbe akabatidzwa nawo.
\v 10 Wakakotamisawo kudenga-denga, akaburuka, nerima guru rakange riri pasi petsoka dzake.
\v 11 Wakatasva kerubhu, akabhururuka; zvirokwazvo, wakaonekwa ari pamapapiro emhepo.
\v 12 Wakazvipoteredza nerima setende, mMvura yakaunganidzwa, nemvumi dzehore dzedenga.
\v 13 Nokupenya, kwakange kuri pamberi pake, mazimbe omoto akabatidzwa.
\v 14 Jehovha wakatinhira kudenga, Wekumusoro-soro wakataura nenzwi rake.
\p
\v 15 Wakatuma miseve, akavaparadza; akatuma mheni, akavavhundusa.
\v 16 Ipapo pasi pegungwa pakaonekwa, uye nheyo dzenyika dzakaratidzwa pachena, nokutuka kwaJehovha, nokufema kwemweya wemhino dzake.
\p
\v 17 Wakatandavadza ruoko rwake ari kumusoro, akanditora, akandinyukura pamvura zhinji.
\v 18 Akandirwira pamuvengi wangu ane simba, nokuna vanondivenga; nokuti vakange vondikurira.
\v 19 Vakandivinga nezuva renjodzi yangu, asi Jehovha wakange ari mutsigiro wangu.
\v 20 Akandibudisira kunzvimbo yakafarikana, akandirwira, nokuti wakange achindifarira.
\p
\v 21 Jehovha wakandiitira zvakaenzana nokururama kwangu, akandipa mubairo wakaenzana nokuchena kwamaoko angu.
\v 22 Nokuti ndakachengeta nzira dzaJehovha, handina kubva kuna Mwari wangu nokunyengera.
\v 23 Nokuti zvese zvaakatonga zvakange zviri pamberi pangu; kana zviri zvaakatema, handina kutsauka kwazviri.
\v 24 Ndakange ndakarurama kwazvo pamberi pake, ndakazvichengeta pazvakaipa zvangu.
\v 25 Naizvozvo Jehovha wakandiitira zvakaenzana nokururama kwangu, zvakaenzana nokuchena kwangu pamberi pake.
\p
\v 26 Ane tsitsi, munomuitirawo tsitsi; munhu, wakarurama kwazvo, munomuitirawo zvakarurama.
\v 27 Wakanaka, munomuitirawo zvakanaka; wakatsauka, munomuitira hasha.
\v 28 Muchaponesa vanhu vanotambudzika, asi meso enyu anoona vanozvikudza kuti muvaderedze.
\v 29 Nokuti muri mwenje wangu, Jehovha; Jehovha uchavhenekera rima rangu.
\v 30 Nokuti nemwi ndichavamba hondo, kana ndina Mwari wangu ndichadarika rusvingo.
\p
\v 31 Kana ari Mwari, nzira yake yakarurama kwazvo; shoko raJehovha rakaidzwa; ndiye nhovo yavese vanotenda kwaari.
\v 32 Nokuti ndiani Mwari, asi iye Jehovha? Ndianiko dombo, asi iye Mwari wedu?
\v 33 Mwari ndiye nhare yangu ine simba; iye unondifambisa nenzira yakarurama.
\v 34 Unoita tsoka dzangu setsoka dzenondokadzi, unondiisa pakakwirira.
\v 35 Unodzidzisa maoko angu kurwa; naizvozvo maoko angu anowembura uta hwendarira.
\v 36 Makandipawo nhovo yokuponesa kwenyu, unyoro hwenyu hwakandikurisa.
\v 37 Makandiitira nzvimbo yakafarikana pasi pangu pandingatsika; tsoka dzangu hadzina kutedzemuka.
\p
\v 38 Ndakateverera vavengi vangu, ndikavaparadza, handina kudzokazve kusvikira vapedzwa.
\v 39 Ndakavapedza, ndakavabaya, havagoni kumuka; vakawira pasi petsoka dzangu.
\v 40 Nokuti makandisunga chiwuno nesimba rokurwa naro; makandikundisa vaindimukira.
\v 41 Makatizisa vavengi vangu, kuti ndiparadze vanondivenga.
\v 42 Vakatarira, asi kwakange kusino muponesi, kuna Jehovha, asi haana kuvapindura.
\v 43 Ipapo ndakavapwanya seguruva renyika; ndikavatswa samatope enzira dzomumusha, ndikavaparadzira kure.
\p
\v 44 Makandirwirawo pakukakavadzana kwavanhu vangu, makandichengeta kuti ndive mukuru wendudzi; vanhu vandakange ndisingazivi, vachandishumira.
\v 45 Vatorwa vachanamata kwandiri; vachateerera pakarepo kana vachindinzwa.
\v 46 Vatorwa vachatorerwa simba, vachabuda pavaivanda vachidedera.
\v 47 Jehovha mupenyu; dombo rangu ngarikudzwe; Mwari, dombo rokuponeswa kwangu, ngaarumbidzwe.
\v 48 Ndiye Mwari unonditsivira, unondikundisa vanhu.
\v 49 Unondibvisa kuvavengi vangu; zvirokwazvo, munondisimudzira kumusoro kwavanondimukira; munondirwira pamunhu unondimanikidza.
\v 50 Naizvozvo ndichakuvongai Jehovha, pakati pendudzi, ndichakudza zita renyu nenziyo.
\v 51 Unopa mambo wake kuponeswa kukuru; uUnoitira muzodzwa wake unyoro, kuna Dhavhidhi navana vake nokusingaperi.
